library("quantmod")

usdjpy <- getSymbols("USD/JPY", src = "oanda", auto.assign = FALSE)

dates <- as.Date(c("2015-05-08", "2015-09-12"), format = "%Y-%m-%d")

  hc_title(text = "Charting some Symbols") %>%

  hc_add_series_xts(eurkpw, id = "eurkpw") %>%
